title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Airbus A330 900neo - version 0.100
description:
In this video we will look at the Native Airbus A330-900 Neo which has been recently updated to version 0.100. The aircraft has the same cockpit as the A32NX from FBW but if you don't have the FBW version installed no problem because this aircraft has it's own copy. The airplane has now been updated to use FBW 0.7.4 and has received several external and internal model updates.

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/18198/airbus-a330-900neo-conversion
